Lunexia 2024-10-19 7:31 p.m.
You can trade 4 resources for 1 with the bank, with a trade port settled its 3 to 1 for you with the bank. If you have a specific port that one resource trades 2 of that resource for 1. Trading in the trade channel requires other players to both have the resource(s) you want, as well as to say yes to the trade, while trading with the bank has no limits and is free
7:32 p.m.
So if you have a humongous income of one specific resource (lets say sheep) and you also own a sheep trade port, you can technically just trade in all your sheep you get over time to just buy everythign else
